Invocation Name: my cat meme
des:
Ask Alexa to open My Cat Meme and she'll give you the definitive quiz on which feline you really are inside.
This multimodal interaction works best with an Echo Show, but is fun to play on any device.

To begin just say:

"Alexa, open My Cat Meme."

or

"Alexa, launch My Cat Meme."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
